summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for the dismissal of proceedings pertaining to certain tracts or parcels of land from that certain condemnation proceeding for the laying off, extending and establishing of 26th Avenue South and other streets and avenues, as provided for by Ordinance No. 60444, being Cause No. 245115 of the Superior Court of the State of Washington for the County of King and repealing a portion of said Ordinance No. 60444.
